super-rich and beautiful.

23
00:02:56,291 --> 00:02:58,333
This is a Host Club?

24
00:02:58,416 --> 00:02:59,875
Oh wow, it's a boy!

25
00:02:59,958 --> 00:03:02,000
Hikaru, Kaoru, I believe
this young man is in

