Whoa. I've heard of
this before.

108
00:06:58,750 --> 00:07:01,791
It's commoner's coffee.
You just add hot water.

109
00:07:01,875 --> 00:07:03,875
I didn't know
there was such a thing!

110
00:07:03,958 --> 00:07:05,750
So it's true then.
Poor people don't even

111
