just because he bought it.

126
00:07:47,583 --> 00:07:51,208
I'm sorry. I was
talking to myself.

127
00:07:53,291 --> 00:07:54,458
Haruhi!

128
00:07:55,375 --> 00:07:57,000
I'm comin'.

129
00:08:06,750 --> 00:08:07,625
Here.

130
00:08:07,708 --> 00:08:09,791
Let the tasting begin!

131
00:08:09,875 --> 00:08:11,791
