to cater to the desires

170
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:14,125
of our guests.

171
00:10:14,208 --> 00:10:15,458
Just so you know,
Tamaki is number one

172
00:10:15,541 --> 00:10:17,250
around here.
He's the king.

173
00:10:17,333 --> 00:10:19,458
