192
00:11:07,958 --> 00:11:10,083
I just don't think
it's all that important.

193
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:13,416
Why should I care about
appearances and labels anyway?

194
00:11:13,500 --> 00:11:15,375
I mean, all that really
matters is what's on

