remember that word.

215
00:11:59,166 --> 00:12:02,166
--I have chosen to share
my expertise with you.

216
00:12:02,250 --> 00:12:04,041
Here's a tip. When
setting down your glass,

217
00:12:04,125 --> 00:12:06,250
