266
00:14:20,500 --> 00:14:25,041
Cute! You're as pretty
as a girl! Adorable!

267
00:14:25,125 --> 00:14:27,000
Haru-chan,
you look so cute!

268
00:14:27,083 --> 00:14:29,000
