turned out well.

297
00:15:45,333 --> 00:15:48,708
And it made me happy
to see my dad enjoy it.

298
00:15:48,791 --> 00:15:50,833
I've had a hard childhood
but Dad and I have

299
00:15:50,916 --> 00:15:53,208
