through okay.

300
00:15:53,291 --> 00:15:54,291
So uh--

301
00:15:54,375 --> 00:15:55,833
Is it okay if tomorrow--

302
00:15:55,916 --> 00:15:57,833
--we request to sit
with you again?

303
00:15:57,916 --> 00:15:59,958
