appreciate that, ladies!

304
00:16:00,041 --> 00:16:01,541
Why's he so popular?

305
00:16:01,625 --> 00:16:02,583
He's a natural.

306
00:16:02,666 --> 00:16:04,041
No training needed.

307
00:16:04,125 --> 00:16:05,625
Have you forgotten about me?

308
00:16:07,958 --> 00:16:10,250
