about our newest host.

310
00:16:13,458 --> 00:16:14,958
Well, that's obvious, Tamaki.

311
00:16:15,041 --> 00:16:17,958
You sure have been
keeping an eye on him.

312
00:16:18,041 --> 00:16:19,125
