to meet someone.

317
00:16:28,666 --> 00:16:32,000
This is my regular guest,
Princess Ayanokoji.

318
00:16:32,083 --> 00:16:34,333
It's that girl
from earlier.

319
00:16:34,416 --> 00:16:36,500
