than for what sex they are.

398
00:21:31,375 --> 00:21:34,083
Well, isn't this an
interesting development?

399
00:21:34,166 --> 00:21:36,125
Oh yeah!

400
00:21:36,208 --> 00:21:38,000
You know, I have to say Senpai,

401
