pretty cool earlier.

402
00:21:46,541 --> 00:21:48,291
Now, I could be wrong,
but I think we may be

403
00:21:48,375 --> 00:21:51,291
witnessing the beginnings
of love here.

404
00:21:51,375 --> 00:21:53,083
